                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "avB53",
                      "fill": "#666666",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "We collect information you provide directly to us, including your name, email address, shipping address, phone number, and payment information when you create an account or place an order. We also automatically collect certain technical data such as your IP address, browser type, and browsing patterns on our site.",
