                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data, including SSL encryption for all transactions and secure server infrastructure. Access to personal information is restricted to authorized personnel only. We conduct regular security audits and maintain compliance with applicable data protection regulations.",
